<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٠ - <span class="c2">(٤٢٥)</span> حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>يُحَدِّثُ عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">« أَقِيمُوا الرُّكُوعَ وَالسُّجُودَ! فَوَاللهِ إِنِّي لَأَرَاكُمْ مِنْ بَعْدِي -<span class="c5"> وَرُبَّمَا قَالَ:</span> مِنْ بَعْدِ ظَهْرِي - إِذَا رَكَعْتُمْ وَسَجَدْتُمْ .»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>